@needles_tokyo_official and @beaver__official are rewriting the rules of everyday dressing with a denim twist on one of the brand's most recognizable silhouettes, the H.D Track Pant. ⁠
⁠
Taking cues from the effortless appeal of Needles' iconic sweats, the collaboration transforms familiar comfort into a new kind of uniform. They come in two colorways: a light blue and a deep black wash. Both are available now via Beaver's online shop and in-store locations.

