@rimowa signature suitcase just became moody.⁠
⁠
The new permanent Ink Blue collection gives the brand’s grooved aluminum luggage a deep midnight finish, joined by matching leather bags, denim travel accessories, and an aluminum card holder. Sydney Lemmon fronts the campaign, carrying the collection through a blue-tinted search for love in Shanghai.

