@ronaldinho and @olaoluslawn just turned football jerseys into one-of-one artworks.⁠
⁠
Created for @ravennafootballclub , the limited capsule features 10 jerseys designed by @giorgiomallone , reworked by Slawn in his London studio, and co-signed by both the artist and Ronaldinho. Less sports merch, more collectible art—with football serving as the canvas.

@adidasy3 has unveiled its Fall/Winter 2026 campaign, enlisting legendary skateboarder and longtime friend of the label Mark Gonzales as its central figure. Captured by photographer Jet Swan during Y-3's presentation at Paris' Palais d’Iéna earlier this year, the campaign pairs Swan’s raw, cinematic lens with Gonzales’ unmistakable presence.⁠
⁠
Wearing key pieces from the Fall/Winter 2026 collection, including Chito-adorned leather, oversized tailoring, denim, and new footwear like the Diagonal Stan Smith, Tokyo Warped, and Nisi High, Gonzales embodies the space where fashion, sport, skate culture, and everyday expression naturally converge. The campaign launched on July 15.

